{
  "stem": "15938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We will take you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was there, when I lived with them, he was big and strong and very-- I didn't ever imagine not to have a protection like him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was very tall and quite a big built man and very authoritative, very, you know, old father' way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it was this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I loved him and dreaded him at the same time because if he came into the room and if you were guilty of anything, we really shook because it was-- and-- and he was very respected in town too.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was confirmed that I was right to be afraid of him or whatever and to think that he is really somebody because all that advice they needed in town, they used to come to us.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not all, but to me it was all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Probably there were other people who gave advise, but I remember people coming and closing the door because they-- they needed money or they needed a doctor or they needed whatever or they needed to make peace between two people.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I watched that, I mean.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was only my father could do that, I thought.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Probably some other people could do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But on the other hand, my mother was very quiet and very fine and small and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think the love between was-- between them was very, very great and a respect for each other.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I think that gives you a lot of security.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She was very gentle, and you know, my father was annoyed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was-- she was always there to protect us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember we would love to sleep in her bed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she was very gentle and the completely opposite of my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She came from Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
